Class
Description
AlertBox
A utility class for creating and displaying standard JavaFX alerts.
Board
Represents a 6x6 Sudoku board with 2x3 blocks.
BoardAdapter
Adapter class that implements the IBoard interface and delegates all operations to a Board instance.
Game
Main game logic class for the Sudoku game.
GameAbstract
Abstract base class for game implementations.

Adapter class that implements the IGame interface and delegates all operations to a Game instance.

Defines the contract for an alert box utility.
IBoard
Interface defining the contract for Sudoku board operations.
IGame
Interface defining the contract for game operations.

A singleton Stage for the main Sudoku game window.

A singleton Stage for the welcome window.

Represents a user/player in the Sudoku game.
